            "element": "span",
            "class": "bld",
            "text": "And upon Judah and Jerusalem.",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "—Which shared in the king’s guilty pride and confidence in the arm of flesh. (Comp. ",
